        "id": 1174099
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-06-08T16:10:50Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This is just decltype(pthread_create)*, why not use that?\n\nThat’s so simple, and you only use it one time, so you don’t even need an extra local type for it. You can just put it into the reinterpret_cast on the next line.\n\nMore reading: https://groups.google.com/a/chromium.org/d/topic/cxx/arOSzjDW7DY",
      "revId": "361dc6356c54c36f8395aafcb189d69783a8c431",
